

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Call Summary & Feedback Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f4f7f9;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c75fe, #1e50d8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .summary-box {
            background: #f4f7f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #444;
            border-left: 5px solid #4c75fe;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e50d8;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c75fe, #1e50d8);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 117, 254, 0.4);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a5fcc, #163ea5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7d7d7d;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .separator {
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #4c75fe;
            margin: 15px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .download-box {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f4f7f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ff5e00);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e07b00, #d14c00);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Call Summary</h1>
            </div>

            <h2>Hello There!</h2>
            <p>Thank you for speaking with us! Here‚Äôs a quick summary of our conversation:</p>

            <div class="separator"></div>

            <div class="summary-box">
                <p><strong>üìÖ Call Date:</strong> {{template_content.call_date}}</p>
                <p><strong>üìå Summary:</strong></p>
                <p class="highlight">"{{template_content.call_summary}}"</p>
                <p><strong>üí≥ CIBIL Score:</strong> {{template_content.cibil_score}}</p>
                <p><strong>üí≥ Type of Loan:</strong> {{template_content.loan_type}}</p>
                <p><strong>üí∞ Eligible Loan Amount:</strong> ‚Çπ{{template_content.loan_amount}}</p>
                <p><strong>üìß Email Address:</strong> {{template_content.email_address}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="download-box">
                <p><strong>‚¨áÔ∏è Download Call Recording:</strong></p>
                <a href="{{template_content.audio_url}}" class="download-btn" download="{{template_content.audio_filename}}">Download Recording</a>
            </div>

            <p>We‚Äôd love to hear your thoughts! How was your experience?</p>

            <a href="{{template_content.feedback_link}}" class="btn">Give Feedback</a>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>Need further assistance? Contact us at <a href="mailto:voiceopsacp@gmail.com">voiceopsacp@gmail.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
